@startuml
state "Account Created" as A
state "Videos Watched" as B
state "Video Uploaded" as C
state "Video Saved" as D
state "Saved Videos Viewed" as E
state "Discussion Entered" as F

A[*] --> B : Create Account
B --> C : Upload Video
C --> D : Save Video
D --> E : View Saved Videos
E --> F : Enter Discussion

@enduml
